.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, water
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking
There 2 different types of food: cauliflower, peas
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, pop
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, september
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, ship
1. the fan of pop is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the person drinking water is the fan of pop##1
3. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Beverage      | 7up        | water   |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | camping |
| Food   | cauliflower     | peas   |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | pop     |
| Birthday           | september        | july    |
| Transport     | motorbike  | ship    |

