.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, sprite
There 2 different types of food: asparagus, pomegranate
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, drama
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, gospel
2 different pets are kept: ferret, snake
There are 2 different favourite colors: aquamarine, grey
1. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the fan of disco##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |
| Beverage      | coffee    | sprite      |
| Food          | asparagus | pomegranate |
| Movie-Genre           | drama     | zombie      |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | disco       |
| Pet           | snake     | ferret      |
| Color     | grey   | aquamarine         |

 